OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK's largest opencast      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcoalmine told it must shut 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's largest opencast coalmine must
OL,6, close after an extension to keep it    
OL,7, running was rejected.                  
OL,9,FIt means production at Ffos-y-Fran,    
OL,10,Fnear Merthyr Tydfil, must now stop     
OL,11,Fafter 16 years of excavation.          
OL,13,FThe operators asked for an extension   
OL,14,Funtil 2024, arguing coal from the mine 
OL,15,Fwas needed by the steel industry.      
OL,17,FBut planning officials advised that the
OL,18,Fproposed extension did not fit with    
OL,19,FWelsh government policies on tackling  
OL,20,Fclimate change.                        
